### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3004/tasks

### Get single task
GET http://localhost:3004/tasks/1

### Task not found (404)
GET http://localhost:3004/tasks/99

### Create task
POST http://localhost:3004/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Learn Error Handling"
}

### Validation error (400)
POST http://localhost:3004/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    
}

### Trigger server error (500)
GET http://localhost:3004/error
